name: GSI Bugaboo Camper Cookset
description: Summon your inner gourmet in the backcountry. This cooking and serving set has it all; non-stick aluminum pots and durable polypropylene dishes.Cookset includes 2 and 3L pots, a frypan, and 2 strainer lids. Nylon lids have silicone rims to withstand high temperatures.Serving set includes four insulated nesting mugs and bowls, with sip lids and four plates.Pot gripper and stuff sack also included.Mugs nest inside bowls, which in turn nest in the 2L pot.Integrated BPA-free strainer lids for draining the pasta or veggies.Stuff sack doubles as a wash basin.
